node.text:
Teaching students how to be an advocate and ally 🏳️‍🌈 can be engaging and creative with this activity! #ad I teamed up with @michaelsstores to help you teach your student about the importance of advocacy.

Be sure to grab all of your favorite multi-colored and alphabet beads for kids at your local Michaels stores for this project with your students! #makeitwithmichaels

#michaelspartner #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram #iteachtoo #teachersofinsta #teachingadvocacy

node.text: Even though our spending habits are VERY different 😅 Ally’s Vow Generator was a great way to learn more about each other’s spending habits and personalities. We are happy to announce we are in a financially open relationship! Head to ally.com/financialvows and share your vows with us in the comments! @ally #financiallyopen #ad

May be an image of text that says '9 tips for supporting LGBTQ+ students @thesuperheroteacher'.

node.text:
🏳️‍⚧️🏳️‍🌈 Double tap this when you’ve read through the tips! Thank you in advance for being an advocate for the LGBTQ+ youth in your classroom. It’s so incredibly important.

You have the capability to create a space that is inclusive and representative and safe for LGBTQ+ students. That’s an incredible power to possess.

Hopefully these tips will help guide you in the right direction when it comes to supporting your students!

#lgbtq #lgbtqrights #safespace #teacherssupportteachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersofig #teacherlife #iteachtoo #classroomdecor #protecttranskids #classroomdesign #classroomsetup

node.text:
Tomorrow, I’m turning 31 🤯🎊, so we are celebrating my birthday this evening! MJ thought she bought a 3, but it was an 8… sooooo I’m actually 81 now 😅.

I’ve learned a lot over the years. I’m not the same person I was 15 years ago… or even one year ago. I believe deeply in the ability for people to change and hope I continue to grow and evolve throughout the years.

Love you all! Cheers 🥂

Happy 2 year anniversary @m_jeltema10! Words cannot describe how much I adore you.

Thank you for:
♥️ loving me deeply
♥️ caring for me infinitely
♥️ showing me a side of you that so many don’t see. You’re my best friend in every sense.

I want you to know that:
♥️ I will love you and cere for you forever.
♥️ you’re going to be the best mom in the entire world
♥️ you’ve made us the luckiest humans on the planet

Thank you for making my world complete. We love you! 😘

node.text:
A look 👀 inside baby SJ’s nursery! It’s all happening so fast… less than 4 weeks to go!!! Who is ready?!?!?

But really… I need y’all to be ready for me haha.

The nursery is honestly a mixture of a whole bunch of things, but mj reallllllyyyy wanted ocean vibes and I wanted something more boho… so we did our best to fuse the two. Honestly, it looks so much cooler and calming in person! I couldn’t seem to capture it with the 📸.

Today has been a day. TIA for all your support!

#nursery #twomoms #twomomsarebetterthanone #twomomsquad #nurserydecor #lgbtparents #lgbtqfamily

node.text:
✈️🌎 Turn your students into world travelers with this informational text resource! With 20+ nonfiction articles ✏️ and corresponding activities/projects, 📓 your students will learn to dissect and annotate while simultaneously learning about different cultures and countries.

I designed this resource to help students strengthen their reading, writing, and analyzing skills. The journal is designed with 20 unique informational text articles (from 20 countries around the world)! Each article is paired with comprehension questions and a variety of activities and projects.

Link to resource in bio: https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Product/Travel-Journal-20-Informational-Text-Articles-Activities-Grades-4-7-DIGITAL-4706090
